  <mainDescription>&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Description&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Modernize applications and the infrastructure, implementing common technologies and consolidating platforms to make the&#xD;
    most efficient use of development and support staff.&lt;br />&#xD;
    &amp;nbsp;&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Symptoms&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Symptoms that indicate the need to optimize resources include:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Multiple&amp;nbsp;development environments/ platforms with siloed development teams.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Each development&amp;nbsp;silo requires its own set of development and collaboration&amp;nbsp;tools.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        Legacy systems require expensive, specialized, hard to find skills to extend and maintain them.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;h3>&#xD;
    Solutions&#xD;
&lt;/h3>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The following solutions help to optimize resources:&lt;br />&#xD;
    &lt;br />&#xD;
    High Impact:&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/determine_app_modernization_strategy_432C5B90.html&quot; guid=&quot;_lZz24LbIEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Determine Application Modernization Strategy&lt;/a> -&amp;nbsp;Create a roadmap to&#xD;
        modernize applications&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/application_transformation_6C08D1F9.html&quot; guid=&quot;_uyUeYLbIEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Application Transformation&lt;/a> - Transform applications using modern architectures&#xD;
        and technologies while leveraging existing investments.&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/rearchitect_for_reuse_503CC74C.html&quot; guid=&quot;_Gc7bsMyEEd6AlLazTePGRg&quot;>Re-Architect for Reuse&lt;/a> - Re-architect existing solutions to improve reusability&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Medium Impact&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;ul>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/application_ui_modernization_88264BD3.html&quot; guid=&quot;_qcHTILbIEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Application UI Modernization&lt;/a>&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;- Extend the value of existing&#xD;
        solutions in a cost effective manner by modernizing their user interfaces&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
    &lt;li>&#xD;
        &lt;a class=&quot;elementLinkWithUserText&quot; href=&quot;./../../publish.bus.practices_for_perf_measurement.base-ibm/guidances/guidelines/application_re-platforming_FDA9E88B.html&quot; guid=&quot;_yVtsoLbIEd6_i8GY7ieNyA&quot;>Application Re-Platforming&lt;/a> - Move applications to more modern platforms&#xD;
    &lt;/li>&#xD;
&lt;/ul></mainDescription>
